0tQpwWJ--21V8YdY4Bqtj_19PNnuSG1dPd2lS5g0ac69PIGaqK0opnLE4V8JJKMEYqwt3tx68RkosYFP8fOYQ7u-Wm4ItYCaOGCdznu1QYWiP5u9K7zXEuhBU9ZjKAG5Qj1M0xuySdj49ooLiGgX81qxbXXQBsK4D59pqyCISWY4IOtgY-yLJY50_3-9M8C7Lmxjmm1Pz0JSbC6daewDYZx5uiTaZdsS6lwV5ZVm5pMlPeaoXenMEjVBB-1LMO0txqFGCSqosRFAO2Tt0-b9JA_9zr0z24N2zWS_6KXJ1Bcg6iMcuXINLXm2XV5m8bxoByEK4_WCWAXCa3OH0x3zTd062cAj7AJQA5yVGIuQTVMu2SJFsR3WCgkRl8plW8tnv6KZUGRh5vfp2_jOAQPVmYy2DvNzB2JMxWdn8RmPaOW_4J3ePMc5DEOvy_DplsADPX2jeyIZr_RpTzTvt6F2zgEiUdfudibaH4X4QNqP-5oLP0cpNfY48CasiGC3WIQ0JHN0P4ZUU41QEJLmtUsxr-O7SQbEbxAwGSaa3ae55zAhap7ZoF5kqhsOHXH-Yf20SC18rZKbpGl2mwyE09w6yOXguSmEk7M6GW4CCz1mTT9lp8At8dS_QcJN21-q1lkiTx9s6nQY6614U5nRm6WpjO-gswrxEoorErsluGunQbHCZ9hTY_DyiJXuUwinH9cYXgW9F5BQnyhomZktkEjiIb6fxmQ-RYHfEvkYnW8Dzp0K3Uu2WExkjkPtbe8nBkVNflm5GBvSKQ0M32cnqv8E5pd2aJLybeGgAd2hi7MIPuQX1ZxMZcWCw23-KXfc-_KA==\\\",\\\"summary\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"summary_text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"**Evaluating contract capabilities**\\\\n\\\\nI’m thinking about a potential functional feature that hasn't been covered. It seems like the \\\\\\\"uses directive\\\\\\\" on contract capabilities declares all Java packages that the contract supplies. This could be something important to consider for ensuring clarity on what's included in the contract. I need to analyze if this directive impacts usability or integration with other functionalities. It really is all about making sure everything is clear and accessible!\\\"}]}\"}, {\"type\": \"toolCall\", \"id\": \"call_MES8FUGB44Fi9z7xKU5XrpXJ|fc_0952a1ca1aaa3c530169f9a131b7f881a29aaa608972851a09\", \"name\": \"edit\", \"arguments\": {\"path\": \"tests/src/org.osgi/org.osgi.namespace.contract/1.0.0/src/test/java/org_osgi/org_osgi_namespace_contract/Org_osgi_namespace_contractTest.java\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"import java.util.ArrayList;\\nimport java.util.LinkedHashMap;\", \"newText\": \"import java.util.ArrayList;\\nimport java.util.Arrays;\\nimport java.util.LinkedHashMap;\"}, {\"oldText\": \"    @Test\\n    void contrac